\q2 M yawa kala tokugwa yoku, kulagi ma bigasi. 
\q1 Yoku kusili om takaikaia odubasi minasina bubuli isim pinupanesi.\f r \ft Kugisi Sam 18.10.\f*\x - \xo 80.1 \xt Sun 25.22\x* 
\q2  
